           fhir:v "/*\n@output: Client is due for Hepatitis A vaccination Guidance\n@guidance: Should vaccinate client with hepatitis A dose as no Hepatitis A dose was administered, client is within appropriate age range and no live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks. \nCheck for contraindications.\n*/\ndefine \"Client is due for Hepatitis A vaccination Guidance\":\n  'Should vaccinate client with hepatitis A dose as no Hepatitis A dose was administered, client is within appropriate age range and no live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks. \nCheck for contraindications.'"
